OL,4,CCern scientist suspended after comments
OL,5, A senior scientist who said physics
OL,6, "was invented and built by men" has
OL,7, been suspended with immediate effect
OL,8, from working with the European nuclear
OL,9, research centre Cern.
OL,11,FProf Alessandro Strumia, of Pisa
OL,12,FUniversity, made the comments during a
OL,13,Fpresentation organised by the group.
OL,15,FHe said, in comments first reported by
OL,16,Fthe BBC's Pallab Ghosh, that physics
OL,17,Fwas "becoming sexist against men".
OL,19,FCern said on Monday it was suspending
OL,20,FProf Strumia pending an investigation.
